## 4.6 Test Environments
- Staging environment with user authentication and session management enabled
- API Gateway endpoint with logging and rejection hooks for invalid payloads
- Mock virus scanning and file validation microservices
- AWS S3 test bucket with access logging
- Network shaping tools to simulate 4G bandwidth and latency

