# 7. Quality Objectives
- Verify upload button visibility for authenticated users only
- Validate rejection of upload attempts by unauthenticated or expired sessions
- Test acceptance of files up to 10MB and rejection of files >=10.01MB
- Confirm only PNG and JPEG files are accepted and properly validated
- Ensure malicious files with spoofed extensions are rejected
- Measure total upload-to-render time does not exceed 2.5 seconds on 4G
- Check that uploaded images appear instantly on the public portfolio grid without manual refresh

