# 9. Risk Mitigation Table
| Risk ID | Description | Impact | Likelihood | Severity | Mitigation Action | Owner |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
|R1|Dynamic database/API connection drops during upload|High|Medium|High|Implement retry logic and alerting for failed uploads|DevOps Lead|
|R2|SLA breach: Upload-to-render exceeds 2.5s on 4G|High|Medium|High|Use JMeter and tcconfig to simulate and optimize for network latency|Performance Engineer|
|R3|Malicious file bypasses header validation|High|Low|High|Integrate OWASP ZAP and enhance backend magic number checks|Security Tester|
|R4|Session expiry not enforced, unauthorized upload attempt|Medium|Low|Medium|Automated negative tests for session state transitions|QA Lead|
|R5|AWS S3 write failures or permission issues|Medium|Low|Medium|Pre-deployment S3 access validation and error logging|DevOps Lead|

